data.title: Britannia :: Indya Foods Pty. Ltd.
data.text: Britannia is one of the most trusted food brands in India. They are the manufacturers of some of India's favorite biscuits, like nutrichoice, good day, milk bikis, Marigold, tiger, etc. The huge product portfolio of the brand ranges from bread cakes biscuit risk to dairy products like beverages, cheese, milk and yogurt. The brand also has a presence in more than 60 countries all over the world. The international footprint of the company includes the Middle East, Africa, Europe, North America, and southeast Asia.
